  <summary date="2021-04-29T16:37:48Z" status="Introduced in House">Rebuild Rural America Act of 2019

This bill directs the Department of Agriculture to establish the Rural Innovation and Partnership Administration and the Rural Future Partnership Fund to provide five-year renewable block grants to certified rural regions to implement locally-developed regional revitalization plans.</summary>
